In thisgame you will play the roll of a german officer " Captain Otto Von Hans ".
It's 06 June 1944. The allied army have launched a large scale amphibious assault on the Axis occupied Normandie,Utah etc in France.
As a brave officer you have to defend your position against the Allied forces on Utah and should not let them pass till your LAST BULLET, LAST MAN, LAST BREATHE.
The reinforcements are on the way.
You have one empty bunker with an MG-42 nad plenty of ammunition.
